{"name":"Jon. Chu","photo":null,"bio":null,"films":[{"id":"yIJj6SnzTdIz","title":"Wicked","year":"2025","stars":3,"genres":["Musical"],"description":"Het onvertelde verhaal van de heksen van Oz en een onwaarschijnlijke vriendschap.","synopsis":"Wicked onthult het onvertelde verhaal van de heksen van Oz en volgt de onwaarschijnlijke vriendschap tussen de onbegrepen, groene Elphaba en de populaire Glinda op Shiz University. Wanneer ze de corruptie van de Tovenaar van Oz ontdekken, komen hun verschillende idealen en lotsbestemmingen met elkaar in botsing. Dit leidt tot een onvermijdelijke breuk die hen uiteindelijk zal transformeren tot de iconische Goede Heks en de Boze Heks van het Westen.","awards":[{"ceremony":"The Oscars","year":"2025","status":"win","category":"Kostuumontwerp","categoryKey":"costume design","entityType":"film","name":"Wicked (2025)"},{"ceremony":"The Oscars","year":"2025","status":"win","category":"Productieontwerp","categoryKey":"production design","entityType":"film","name":"Wicked (2025)"},{"ceremony":"The Oscars","year":"2024","status":"win","category":"Kostuumontwerp","categoryKey":"costume design","entityType":"film","name":"Wicked (2025)"},{"ceremony":"The Oscars","year":"2024","status":"win","category":"Productieontwerp","categoryKey":"production design","entityType":"film","name":"Wicked (2025)"},{"ceremony":"Critics choice","year":"2025","status":"win","category":"Kostuumontwerp","categoryKey":"costume design","entityType":"film","name":"Wicked (2025)"},{"ceremony":"Critics choice","year":"2025","status":"win","category":"Productieontwerp","categoryKey":"production design","entityType":"film","name":"Wicked (2025)"},{"ceremony":"The Oscars","year":"2025","status":"nomination","category":"Beste film (drama)","categoryKey":"best picture drama","entityType":"film","name":"Wicked (2025)"},{"ceremony":"The Oscars","year":"2025","status":"nomination","category":"Geluid","categoryKey":"sound","entityType":"film","name":"Wicked (2025)"},{"ceremony":"The Oscars","year":"2025","status":"nomination","category":"Make-up & Hair","categoryKey":"make up and hair","entityType":"film","name":"Wicked (2025)"},{"ceremony":"The Oscars","year":"2025","status":"nomination","category":"Montage","categoryKey":"film editing","entityType":"film","name":"Wicked (2025)"},{"ceremony":"The Oscars","year":"2025","status":"nomination","category":"Soundtrack","categoryKey":"music score","entityType":"film","name":"Wicked (2025)"},{"ceremony":"The Oscars","year":"2025","status":"nomination","category":"Visuele effecten","categoryKey":"visual effects","entityType":"film","name":"Wicked (2025)"}],"awardSummary":{"wins":6,"nominations":6}},{"id":"Gj99u0a4RRVg","title":"Wicked: For Good","year":"2025","stars":2,"genres":["Musical"],"description":"Het slot van de tweedelige verfilming van *Wicked* in Oz.","synopsis":"In *Wicked: For Good*, het spectaculaire slotstuk van de tweedelige verfilming, volgen we de uiteenlopende paden van Elphaba en Glinda in het land van Oz. Terwijl Elphaba als de 'Wicked Witch of the West' in ballingschap leeft en strijdt tegen de corruptie van de Tovenaar, is Glinda uitgegroeid tot het populaire symbool van goedheid in de Emerald City. Hun vriendschap wordt tot het uiterste beproefd door politieke intriges, persoonlijke offers en de onverwachte komst van een meisje uit Kansas. Uiteindelijk moeten de twee heksen hun gedeelde verleden onder ogen zien om de toekomst van Oz en zichzelf voorgoed te veranderen.","awards":[{"ceremony":"The Oscars","year":"2025","status":"nomination","category":"Productieontwerp","categoryKey":"production design","entityType":"film","name":"Wicked: For Good (2025)"},{"ceremony":"Critics choice","year":"2026","status":"nomination","category":"Beste film (drama)","categoryKey":"best picture drama","entityType":"film","name":"Wicked: For Good (2025)"},{"ceremony":"Critics choice","year":"2026","status":"nomination","category":"Kostuumontwerp","categoryKey":"costume design","entityTyp